# 🤖 Robot Security System — Lưu đồ dự án

## 1. Lưu đồ tổng quan — Kiến trúc hệ thống

```mermaid
graph TB
    subgraph "🔌 ESP32 Hardware"
        CAM["📷 ESP32-CAM<br/>(station/)<br/>OV3660 Camera"]
        MOTOR["⚙️ ESP32 Motor<br/>(SIN/)<br/>TB6612 + Sensors"]
    end

    subgraph "🖥️ Server (Docker)"
        TCP["🔗 TCP Receiver<br/>:8765"]
        YOLO["🧠 YOLOv8n<br/>Person/Pet Detection"]
        SERVO["🎯 Servo Controller<br/>Pan/Tilt Simulation"]
        API["🌐 FastAPI<br/>:8000"]
        MQTT_S["📡 MQTT Client"]
        DB["🗄️ PostgreSQL<br/>:5432"]
        TELE["📱 Telegram Bot"]
    end

    subgraph "📡 MQTT Broker"
        MOSQUITTO["🦟 Mosquitto<br/>:1883"]
    end

    subgraph "👤 User Interface"
        WEB["🌍 Web Dashboard<br/>localhost:8000"]
        FLUTTER["📱 Flutter App<br/>Android/iOS"]
    end

    CAM -->|"TCP :8765<br/>[4B len][JPEG]"| TCP
    TCP -->|"frame_queue"| YOLO
    YOLO -->|"detections"| SERVO
    SERVO -->|"pan, tilt"| MQTT_S
