## Tổng kết cấu trúc file

| Thành phần | Thư mục | Ngôn ngữ | Mô tả |
|------------|---------|-----------|--------|
| **ESP32-CAM** | `station/` | C (ESP-IDF) | Chụp JPEG, gửi TCP, stream MJPEG |
| **ESP32 Motor** | `SIN/` | C (ESP-IDF) | Motor TB6612, VL53L0X, PIR, MQTT |
| **Server** | [server/](file:///D:/ROBOT/server/server.py#131-152) | Python | YOLO, TCP, MQTT, FastAPI, PostgreSQL |
| **Flutter App** | `flutter_application/` | Dart | Dashboard, Control, Settings, Camera |
| **Shared Config** | [shared_config.h](file:///D:/ROBOT/shared_config.h) | C Header | WiFi SSID, Server IP (dùng chung) |
| **Docker** | [server/docker-compose.yml](file:///D:/ROBOT/server/docker-compose.yml) | YAML | PostgreSQL + Mosquitto + Server |
